						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">sdwave wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">; ===============================================<br />; Interrupt handlers<br />; ===============================================<br />irq:<br />multiLineIrq:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; php&nbsp; &nbsp;;push flags<br /><br />...<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; plp&nbsp; &nbsp;;pull flags<br /><br />&nbsp; &nbsp; rti<br /></div></div><br />Not related to your actual question (I don't have time to go through the code right now), but a small detail: you don't need to push and restore the flags, 6502 will do that automatically.</div>

					
