			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Writing to $2000 requires having the other bits correct (background pattern table base address, sprite size and pattern table base address if 8x8, and NMI). Writing to $2005/first needs to be done in horizontal blank if the fine X scroll ($2005/first bits 2-0) will be changing at all. So I'm with tokumaru: $2006 first is probably the best option.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

